LOCUS       tRNA-gRNA_position_[D1_n-1]_(GB1208) 3222 bp    DNA     circular SYN 15-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  tRNA and scaffold for the assembly of GBoligomers for the first
            position (positon [D1_n-1]) of a polycistronic tRNA-gRNA regulated
            by the U6-26 or U6-1 promoter (2-part multiplexing).
